{"tid":601292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"cls 頭先銀行職員話最多存現金五萬，又話要揾主任來🔥","createTime":"2018-03-22T06:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T10:13:10.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"eaa86ba2e1e7b534bcfb707bb4fb5765b8bc5e5f","tid":601292,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"我去入現金七萬<br />\n櫃檯職員話最多入五萬<br />\n叫我其餘要拎去櫃員機入<br />\n<br />\n我：我咪要排多一次隊？<br />\n職：櫃員機而家無人<br />\n我：我未用過機入現金<br />\n職：陣間我揾個同事幫你去櫃員機入<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我費時理佢，將七萬現金放係佢面前<br />\n職(死死地氣）：好啦，我今次幫你入<br />\n我：你地無任何告示話「最多入五萬」🔥<br />\n<br />\n佢數完錢，係電腦入完數後又話<br />\n職：要揾主任來睇睇<br />\n<br />\n隔咗一陣，主任都未出現<br />\n<br />\n職：可唔可以講吓呢筆錢的來源<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：來自屋企人的<br />\n<br />\n跟住又問我拎身份証睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我(一邊拎身份証一邊同佢講）：而家係入七萬，唔係入七百萬喎(暗示佢小題大做)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後搞掂哂<br />\n職：唔好意思，阻你咁多時間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d58aa358970dcb68a6a72ed052a20368c3a1d2","tid":601292,"uid":40470,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"見你樣衰似賊先會咁"},{"pid":"a228dd8e7ce1853f65f07ddfb0efcbf624a5c046","tid":601292,"uid":31672,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:16:46.000Z","msg":"銀行呢方面不嬲on9<br />\n利申做過兩個月teller"},{"pid":"eccfdede017157eadff78d2c6a3feee6c14de30d","tid":601292,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTi